# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# ── Dependencies ──────────────────────────────────────────────
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# ── Testing ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
/coverage

# ── Build outputs ─────────────────────────────────────────────
/.next/
/out/
/build
dist/

# ── OS junk ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.pem
Thumbs.db

# ── Debug ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*
*.log

# ── Secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env*
!.env.example

# ── Deployment ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vercel
netlify.toml

# ── TypeScript / Config ──────────────────────────────────────
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
server.pid
*.tgz

# ── Personal Data Protection ─────────────────────────────────
# Personal user data lives at ~/.journey/data/ — NOT in this repo.
# Never write personal roadmap data to this directory.
# The only tracked file is the starter template (explicitly allowed below).
data/*
!data/roadmap.json

# Never commit personal data directories
.journey/
.journey_data/
*.personal.json
*_personal.json
